</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/unikirose.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nikirose</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://NoirDaila.homestead.com/files/Laney/america.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(8/5/02 11:00:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=588.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.extremezone.com/~medieval/buttons/bloodsword.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_sad.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: When loved ones die.</span><hr size=1> Thank you to Everyone who has given their kind thoughts.<br>
